      <title>Nvidia、DuckDuckGo 在新一轮融资中支持 AI 搜索初创公司 You.com</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/nvidia-duckduckgo-back-ai-search-startup-you-com-in-new-round</link>
